{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MINIMALIST STRATEGY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enjoy minimalist, action-packed strategy game</strong> with simplified city building, upgrades, and troop management so you can focus more on tactical gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/Fullmoon_siege.gif?t=1739274948\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PICK YOUR FACTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each faction offers <strong>distinct playstyles and has unique heroes</strong>, resource management, troops, and upgrades. Counter your opponent with over 30 different troops, or outsmart them by using the environment to your advantage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/CC_Factions.jpg?t=1739274948\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the Monceaux, <strong>a religious kingdom of knights and warriors.</strong> Their versatile troops and strong siege make them easy to pick up but hard to master.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join the Fahad, <strong>a nomadic culture harnessing the power of the elements</strong>. Their fast, high-damage troops and impactful elementals cause many unexpected situations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or guide the URA, <strong>a republic of scientists and mechanics</strong>. They compensate for their lack of speed and protection with tactical superiority and pure firepower!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/Fire_rain.gif?t=1739274948\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>HANDCRAFTED CAMPAIGNS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enjoy a handcrafted campaign for each faction</strong>, with missions dedicated to their unique playstyle and troops. Guide a paranoid king, a lost shaman, and a grumpy general as they rampage over the lands with ever-changing alliances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/Fahad_empire.gif?t=1739274948\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build your empire and set up your defenses</strong>. Train a huge army to perform a powerful strike, raid your opponent with hit-and-run tactics, or level up your hero for them to become a one-man army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/Fahad_empire.gif?t=1739274948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2838160?t=1739274948","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739274948","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/45beab4a9ba649a7146e692fabd2c616a2ad8433/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739274948","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/45beab4a9ba649a7146e692fabd2c616a2ad8433/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739274948","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MINIMALIST STRATEGY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enjoy minimalist, action-packed strategy game</strong> with simplified city building, upgrades, and troop management so you can focus more on tactical gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/Fullmoon_siege.gif?t=1739